    - PARENT LINKAGE: p is derived from the parent SCAN NUMBER (Master Scan Number trailer, falling back to scan-string parent) mapped through a `scanNumber -> emitted ordinal` map maintained during the loop. If the parent MS1 was FILTERED OUT / not emitted (no entry in the map), set precursor_index (and precursor_id) NULL but STILL emit the precursor/selected_ion entry.
